Package: demeter
Version: __VERSION__
Architecture: __ARCH__
Maintainer: Sam Chilton <sam@chilton.tv>
Section: net
Priority: optional
Depends: adduser
Description: Bulk programmer for GV UCP/IQ broadcast cards
 Demeter is a headless server that speaks the RollCall protocol natively (no
 RollTrak.exe) and hosts a web GUI for bulk-configuring Grass Valley UCP/IQ
 cards across many frames. It installs as a systemd service ('demeter')
 listening on port 8080, storing its data under /var/lib/demeter.
